## Recurring date field

This field type most suitable for Events allows adding multiple dates and date ranges and set recurring intervals for each

## General options

- Field name
- Field key
- Description
- Is Required
- CSS Classes

## Specific options

- **Enable multiple dates:** Allows adding multiple dates
- **Maximum number of dates allowed:** Set the number of dates allowed if multiple dates are enabled
- **Enable recurring dates:** Enable options to configure recurring dates based on specific interval
- **Enable time picker:** Select start and end time in addition to date(s)
